snippet.title: Brazilian Front End Dev Switch to iOS Mobile - App Review: MyMovies
snippet.description:
Let's do another iOS app review, this time submitted to me by Leo Modro called MyMovies.  You can find it here: https://itunes.apple.com/US/app/id1291144826?mt=8
Some various bugs but overall it's a pretty solid way to look up the latest movies that are interesting. Enjoy.
